data.description: This single owner home offers a versatile open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and one half bath. The entry leads to a flexible space that could be formal dining or a study. The remainder of the downstairs is a large open area with kitchen, dining, and living rooms all displaying the beautiful pond view in the back yard. The kitchen boasts granite counters and stainless appliances with ample cabinet space and a generous island. The upstairs includes a flex loft area that could be enclosed for a 5th bedroom or used as-is for additional living space, office, or game room. The primary bedroom has a large walk in closet with custom built ins, and the bathroom includes a garden tub with a pond view, and a separate shower. In the back is a 10 x 11 Screened lanai and a 10 x 16 open air brick paver patio great for BBQ and entertaining. Recent updates include some plumbing fixtures, new carpet, new paint downstairs, and a new water softener system. This home is situated with a wooded buffer on one side and pond in the rear making it a very private and peaceful setting. Mission Trace is walking distance to St Johns River State College, the nearby Publix shopping center and restaurants. Approx 3 miles to I95 for an easy commute, and minutes to downtown and the beaches.
